        "description": "<p><em>To-Fu Fury</em> is a fast action platform game where the player controls a slab of tofu. He has to pass the obstacles and defeat enemies (bandits and ninjas) and besides the fact that Tofu is ninja, he uses mainly his 'tofu' powers to progress. Tofu can perform super jumps that can destroy many enemies at the same time. He can also stick to wooden surface, even on ceilings, slide down on jade which makes him really fast, and ricochet on metal plates which improves damage he deals to enemies.</p>\n<p>You can control the camera position using the Fire Phone camera, control movement of To-Fu using two-finger tap and drag Tofu to jump on longer distances. The game has different areas with multiple levels each. The last one is made of challenges that can be unlocked or bought. Each area ends with final boss; defeating him unlocks the next area.</p>\n<p>The game offers an in-game shop where you can buy additional skins and levels through in-app purchases. Boosts are available to buy for tougher levels.</p>",
